    l.add(new LessonModel(
      description: "Work on what is good for you",
      group: "Mindfulness",
      title: "Increasing the power of mindfulness",
      stagenumber: 1,
      text: {
        "1": {
          "text":
              "Increasing the power of consciousness it’s a lot like weight training. You simply do exercises where you practice sustaining close attention and peripheral awareness at the same time."
        },
        "2": {
          "text":
              "Like strengthening a muscle developing powerful mindfulness involves enhancing a natural capacity that we all have.  "
        },
        "3": {
          "text":
              "Just reflect for a moment how your mind changes throughout a day. Sometimes we feel quite sharp, energetic and lucid. On the other end, there are times when we feel sluggish."
        },
        "4": {
          "text":
              "A lack of mental energy leads to dullness or drowsiness. Imagine that we could train our mind to always feel sharp, energetic and lucid..."
        },
      },
    ));

